To see how container networking works with and without service discovery, try the [Cats and Dogs](https://github.com/cloudfoundry/cf-networking-examples) example in the Container-to-Container Networking Release repository. In this tutorial, you deploy two apps and create a Container-to-Container Networking policy that allows them to communicate directly with each other.